OL,3,C'Just chaos': Man diagnosed with
OL,4,Ccancer after spending three days in ED
OL,5,Ccorridor
OL,7,F"And then obviously you have another 9
OL,8,Fpeople in your row of chairs, so
OL,9,Fthey're all getting up and moving and
OL,10,Fshifting and speaking to their family
OL,11,Fon the phone or whatever they're doing.
OL,13,F"You never got a minute."
OL,15,FWhen David was finally admitted to a
OL,16,Fward, he was diagnosed with lung
OL,17,Fcancer and had to process the news
OL,18,Fwith very little privacy.
