OL,3,C'Just chaos': Man diagnosed with
OL,4,Ccancer after spending three days in ED
OL,5,Ccorridor
OL,7,F"Everywhere you went there were people
OL,8,Fjust in the corridors. The staff were
OL,9,Fdoing their best," he said.
OL,11,F"Anytime you tried to go anywhere, you
OL,12,Fwere trying not to wake up this person
OL,13,Fand that person."
OL,15,F"And no privacy, no screens, nothing
OL,16,Flike that."
OL,18,FThe day after his diagnosis, David had
OL,19,Fsurgery to remove the cancerous tumor.
