OL,3,C'Just chaos': Man diagnosed with
OL,4,Ccancer after spending three days in ED
OL,5,Ccorridor
OL,7,FHad he not gone to the emergency
OL,8,Fdepartment, he believes that it could
OL,9,Fhave been much longer before his
OL,10,Fcancer was diagnosed and treatment
OL,11,Fcould begin.
OL,13,FA new report into corridor care by the
OL,14,FRoyal College of Nursing warns that
OL,15,Fthis type of treatment is now
OL,16,Fcommonplace, with nurses describing
OL,17,Fthe conditions for patients as
OL,18,F"torture".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
