OL,3,C'Just chaos': Man diagnosed with
OL,4,Ccancer after spending three days in ED
OL,5,Ccorridor
OL,7,FThe RCN's Rita Devlin said: "Those
OL,8,Fpatients are being forced to sit
OL,9,Fupright in chairs for for three or
OL,10,Ffour days, and that's where they eat,
OL,11,Fthat's where they sleep, and that's
OL,12,Fwhere they try and have some dignity
OL,13,Fand privacy.
OL,15,F"So it is shocking that that we're at
OL,16,Fthis position.
OL,18,F"And the staff who are caring for
OL,19,Fthem, I am really concerned about
OL,20,Ftheir health and wellbeing."
