OL,3,C'Just chaos': Man diagnosed with
OL,4,Ccancer after spending three days in ED
OL,5,Ccorridor
OL,7,FIn a statement, the Department of
OL,8,FHealth said: "No-one wants to see sick
OL,9,Fpeople being treated in corridors but
OL,10,Fsadly, we have a finite capacity and
OL,11,Fsevere pressures arise when hospitals
OL,12,Fare forced to operate often well
OL,13,Fbeyond capacity."
OL,15,FIt added that there is "no quick fix
OL,16,Fbut the only medium to long term
OL,17,Fsolution is to reduce demand and
OL,18,Fmanage demand differently."
